<li class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant flex items-center gap-xs"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px] text-primary">check</span> All uploads are encrypted</li>
<li class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant flex items-center gap-xs"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px] text-primary">check</span> We never share your data with third parties</li>
<li class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant flex items-center gap-xs"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px] text-primary">check</span> GDPR compliant</li>
<li class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant flex items-center gap-xs"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px] text-primary">check</span> You can delete analyses anytime</li>
<li class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant flex items-center gap-xs"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px] text-primary">check</span> No data retention beyond what you choose</li>
